305
00:21:13,660 --> 00:21:14,380
Liu.

306
00:21:14,820 --> 00:21:16,060
Why are you out of bed?

307
00:21:17,180 --> 00:21:18,380
I am here for some fresh air.

308
00:21:18,860 --> 00:21:20,020
Did you tell the doctor?

309
