The doctor said it's okay.
I'll just have to be careful.

310
00:21:24,940 --> 00:21:25,700
How do you feel?

311
00:21:26,740 --> 00:21:28,860
I don't feel anything right now.

312
00:21:29,100 --> 00:21:30,100
But Dong,

313
00:21:30,100 --> 00:21:32,620
